def transform(sequence):
    ones = sequence.index('1') if '1' in sequence else len(sequence)
    zeros = sequence[ones:].index('0') if '0' in sequence[ones:] else len(sequence) - ones
    return sequence[ones:ones+zeros] + sequence[:ones] + sequence[ones+zeros:]
